    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="zh-CN"><head>  <meta charset="UTF-8">  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">  <title>高考后的第一次旅行</title></head><body>  <article class="blog-content">    <h3>探索云南</h3>    <p>2022.7.17-2022.7.27</p>    <h4>丽江古城</h4>    <p>古城很大 好逛 有意思</p>    <center>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-1.jpg" alt="丽江古城1" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-2.jpg" alt="丽江古城2" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;"/>    </center>    <h4>茶马古道-玉龙雪山</h4>    <p>玉龙雪山没有开放 远远望了一下 不过很漂亮</p>    <center>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-3.jpg" alt="茶马古道" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-4.jpg" alt="玉龙雪山1" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-5.jpg" alt="玉龙雪山2" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-6.jpg" alt="玉龙雪山3" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-7.jpg" alt="茶马古道2" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;"/>    </center>    <h4>大理</h4>    <p>理想邦超级多人拍照比较出片，白天去的大理古城没啥感觉</p>    <center>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-8.jpg" alt="理想邦" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-9.jpg" alt="大理古城" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>    </center>        <p>调皮一下</p>    <center>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-14.jpg" alt="大理酒店" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;"/>    </center>    <h4>西双版纳</h4>    <p>版纳在本次旅途中给我的体验很好，仅仅次于第一天到的丽江古城</p>    <center>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-10.jpg" alt="西双版纳1" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-11.jpg" alt="西双版纳2" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-12.jpg" alt="西双版纳3" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom: 20px;"/>        <img src="/images/yunnan/yn-13.jpg" alt="西双版纳4" style="zoom:65%;border-radius:8px;"/>    </center>  </article></body></html>]]></content>
    
    
